name: Feed your Cell
description:
Feed your Cell is my first attempt in making a game for mobiles, trying it out as a webGL launch at first for presentation and fixing bugs submitted by the community.

You must defend the cell in the middle of the screen, while feeding it with nutrients for points, after certain amount of points, you can unlock a new look for your cell and environment.

Have fun and any doubt, word or bug, contact me at joselarmenta@proton.me.

Thanks!
